ad crumbs. Transfer to prepared baking sheet."},{"content":"Heat oil to fry in a small pot over medium heat (see Tip)."},{"content":"Fry croquettes in small batches until golden brown (approx. 2 min. per batch). Transfer to paper towels to drain. Allow to cool slightly, garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If mixture is too soft to shape, add an additional 2 tbsp of bread crumbs.","Serve with cranberry sauce or gravy.","For crispy, golden results: use a thermometer to ensure oil temperature is maintained between 350°F-375°F."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","55m","22 pieces"]}